    "Begin your visit with a celebratory wine toast aboard the train, surrounded by stunning vineyards under the limitless Napa sky. Or enjoy the stretch of rolling vineyards from a high point in the sky, an unobstructed view of the vineyard's great vastness contributing a sensation of peaceful anticipation."
